ulak (0.0.2-2PIGSTY) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Align the DEB compatibility patch with RPM.
  * Fall back to curl_multi_wait() on builders with older libcurl headers.
  * Enable the Redis dispatcher only when the distro libhiredis-dev package
    ships hiredis_ssl.h, so Debian 12 and Ubuntu 22 keep building.

 -- Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>  Sun, 19 Apr 2026 09:30:00 +0800

ulak (0.0.2-1PIGSTY) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Carry the shared 0.0.2 hiredis compatibility patch used by RPM.
  * Enable the HTTP, Kafka, MQTT, Redis, and AMQP dispatchers to match RPM.
  * Remove shared PGXS docs from the postgresql-doc namespace.

